{"tid":251949,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（有片）阿根廷少年fb直播玩獵槍　疑走火誤轟斃友人","createTime":"2017-05-21T11:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-21T12:39:18.000Z","uid":41351,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6781059514626fdac9294f12ff86eb8db98c5da6","tid":251949,"uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T11:00:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lqSm8MqQgmk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlqSm8MqQgmk&d=zEdRUiHPsyXb%2F8eFbI6WSNWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=9999937e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lqSm8MqQgmk</a><br />\n阿根廷一名12歲少年日前與一名朋友在家中耍樂，期間開啟facebook的直播功能。少年其後拿起父親的獵槍把玩，並作勢指向其女友人，詎料獵槍疑走火，射中女友人的頭部，令她當場死亡。警方現正調查事件，並暫時歸類案件為意外。 <br />\n<br />\n阿根廷東北部地區一名少年與12歲女友人維加（Georgina Magali Vega）回家玩耍，又開啟facebook直播他們的玩樂過程。男童一度拿起父親的獵槍，指着維加的頭部，並稱：「殺我吧！不然我就殺你」但獵槍疑在玩耍期間走火，令維加頭部中槍身亡。<br />\n<br />\n事發後，在場的其他友人隨即跑出屋外求救，而鄰居聽到槍聲後報警求助。醫護人員到現場時，發現維加倒卧血泊，返魂乏術。 <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170518/mobile/bknint-20170518233130054-0518_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170518%2Fmobile%2Fbknint-20170518233130054-0518_17011_001.html&d=zEdRUiHPsyXb%2F8eFbI6WSNWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=3fac115a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170518/mobile/bknint-20170518233130054-0518_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"1ef3450b3921ed8c89254f175766b5a98b448d27","tid":251949,"uid":9292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T12:03:28.000Z","msg":"唔敢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e736c2c0437d1dd7eafb9d2af61e804ba6876b4","tid":251949,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T12:09:30.000Z","msg":"rip<br />\n<br />\n冇睇"},{"pid":"07dce476e31984c0906816fdc42af01b1dd9f84d","tid":251949,"uid":82175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T12:11:58.000Z","msg":"無